"title": "1105: God, power of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1105: god, power of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God is all-powerful (that is omnipotent), and is able to do whatever he wills. His power is limited only by his character.</p>\n<h2>God is all-powerful</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:27\">MRK 10:27</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:26\">MAT 19:26</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:14\">GEN 18:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps93:1\">PSA 93:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:36\">MRK 14:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:37\">LUK 1:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:7\">2CO 4:7</a></p>\n<h2>God cannot be thwarted</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:2\">JOB 42:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:12\">JOB 9:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:27\">ISA 14:27</a></p>\n<h2>God's names denote his power</h2>\n<h3>The uniqueness of God's power</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:6\">JER 10:6</a></strong></p>\n<h3>He is the Almighty</h3>\n<p><code>the Almighty'' is Hebrew</code>El Shaddai'':\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:3\">GEN 28:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:11\">GEN 35:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:14\">GEN 43:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:3\">EXO 6:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job11:7\">JOB 11:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:2\">JOB 31:2</a></p>\n<h3>He is the LORD Almighty and God Almighty</h3>\n<p><code>Almighty'' in these verses is usually Hebrew</code>Sabaoth'':\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:10\">PSA 24:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:8\">PSA 89:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:16\">JER 10:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:18\">2CO 6:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:17\">REV 11:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:6\">REV 19:6</a></p>\n<h3>He is the Mighty One</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:24\">GEN 49:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:22\">JOS 22:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:1\">PSA 50:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:24\">ISA 1:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:21\">ISA 10:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:16\">ISA 60:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:62\">MRK 14:62</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:49\">LUK 1:49</a></p>\n<h2>God's power is seen above all in his acts of redemption</h2>\n<h3>God is powerful to save</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:17\">ZEP 3:17</a></strong></p>\n<h3>God shows his power in the exodus</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:29\">DEU 9:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:9\">EXO 13:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:31\">EXO 14:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:8\">DEU 7:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:26\">DEU 9:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:10\">NEH 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:21\">JER 32:21</a></p>\n<h3>God shows his power through the work of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:24\">ACT 2:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:4\">ROM 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:19-Eph1:21\">EPH 1:19–1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:13-Col2:15\">COL 2:13–2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:10\">REV 12:10</a></p>\n<h3>God shows his power through the proclamation of the good news about Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:16\">ROM 1:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:18\">1CO 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:24-1Cor1:25\">1CO 1:24–1:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:4\">2CO 10:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:12\">COL 2:12</a></p>\n<h2>God's power is shown in Jesus Christ's life</h2>\n<h3>God's power in Jesus Christ's earthly ministry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:17\">LUK 5:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:19\">LUK 6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:46\">LUK 8:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:38\">ACT 10:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:16\">2PE 1:16</a></p>\n<h3>God's power in Jesus Christ's heavenly ministry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:16\">HEB 7:16</a></strong> <em>In contrast to all other priests, Jesus Christ exercises his ministry now in heaven because death could not hold him.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:10\">ACT 4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:4\">2CO 13:4</a></p>\n<h3>God's power seen in Jesus Christ's second coming</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:26\">MRK 13:26</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:30\">MAT 24:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:27\">LUK 21:27</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:9-2Thess1:10\">2TH 1:9–1:10</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit demonstrates God's power</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:8\">MIC 3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:38\">ACT 10:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:19\">ROM 15:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:4-1Cor2:5\">1CO 2:4–2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:5\">1TH 1:5</a></p>\n<h2>God's power in the world</h2>\n<h3>God rules the created order</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:20\">ROM 1:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:1\">PSA 19:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps65:6\">PSA 65:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:34\">PSA 68:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:26\">ISA 40:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:26\">MAT 8:26</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:39\">MRK 4:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:19\">MAT 21:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3\">HEB 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>God's works are powerful</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut3:24\">DEU 3:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:18\">PSA 71:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:12\">PSA 77:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:4\">PSA 145:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:17-Jer32:19\">JER 32:17–32:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:51\">LUK 1:51</a></p>\n<h3>The ark symbolises God's powerful presence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:8\">PSA 132:8</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:41\">2CH 6:41</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam5:1-1Sam5:12\">1SA 5:1–5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:6-2Sam6:8\">2SA 6:6–6:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:11-2Sam6:12\">2SA 6:11–6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:61\">PSA 78:61</a></p>\n<h3>God keeps his promises</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:21\">ROM 4:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:8\">2CO 9:8</a></p>\n<h3>God gives life to the dead</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:14\">1CO 6:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:29\">MAT 22:29</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:24\">MRK 12:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:21\">PHP 3:21</a></p>\n<h2>God's power in the lives of believers</h2>\n<h3>God gives his own power to his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:11-1Chr29:12\">1CH 29:11–29:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:10\">1SA 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:27-Dan2:28\">DAN 2:27–2:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:3-2Cor13:4\">2CO 13:3–13:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:13\">PHP 4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:7\">2TI 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:11\">1PE 4:11</a></p>\n<h3>God's power achieves his purposes in his people's lives</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:11\">2TH 1:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:4\">MIC 5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:28\">ACT 4:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:4\">1CO 5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:20-Eph1:21\">EPH 1:20–1:21</a></p>\n<h3>God's power completes his work of salvation in believers' lives</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:5\">1PE 1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:12\">2TI 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:25\">HEB 7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:24\">JUD 1:24</a></p>\n<h3>God's power gives believers inner strength</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:16-Eph3:17\">EPH 3:16–3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:18-Eph1:19\">EPH 1:18–1:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:10\">EPH 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:10\">PHP 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:11\">COL 1:11</a></p>\n<h3>God's power is made plain through human weakness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:9-2Cor12:10\">2CO 12:9–12:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:1-Isa53:3\">ISA 53:1–53:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:7\">2CO 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:4\">2CO 13:4</a></p>\n<h3>God's power gives help to believers in suffering</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:16-2Tim4:17\">2TI 4:16–4:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:8\">2CH 25:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:1\">PSA 46:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:17\">DAN 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:7\">2CO 6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:8\">2TI 1:8</a></p>\n<h2>God's power is limited only by his character</h2>\n<h3>God cannot deny himself</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:13\">2TI 2:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:17\">JAS 1:17</a></p>\n<h3>God cannot tolerate evil</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:13\">HAB 1:13</a></strong></p>\n<h3>God cannot be tempted</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:13\">JAS 1:13</a></strong></p>\n<h3>God cannot lie</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num23:19\">NUM 23:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:29\">1SA 15:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:18\">HEB 6:18</a></p>\n<h2>God's power is to be praised</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:35\">PSA 68:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps21:13\">PSA 21:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:14\">PSA 118:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:16\">1TI 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:25\">JUD 1:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:12\">REV 5:12</a></p>",
